{{Quote|The rendezvous is no problem. We simply need to get to the rendezvous site and say, Oh, no, we're all down with the Tastiged Flu. Sure, come over. Hope you don't mind when we have sneezing fits all over you and infect you.|Ton Phanan, to Wedge Antilles|<ref name="Wraith">''[[X-Wing: Wraith Squadron]]''</ref>}}
The '''Tastiged Flu''' was a highly contagious flu from the [[Tastiged system/Legends|Tastiged system]].

{{Stub}}

==Behind the scenes==
The Tastiged Flu was mentioned in [[X-Wing: Wraith Squadron|''Wraith Squadron'']], [[Aaron Allston]]'s [[1998]] fifth installment of the [[Star Wars: X-Wing (novel series)|''Star Wars: X-Wing'' novel series]].<ref name="Wraith" />

